Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.96,0:17:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你得逞的 高卢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就用这光辉 斩灭尔等虫豸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武神光临剑！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 抵挡住了我的武神光临剑？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听吧 听我猎户座的咆哮！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猎户绝灭！
