Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞翔吧 天马座
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早已告诉你
