Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的虫豸们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.08,0:19:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群小鬼
